name: "Flaming sword" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
My mind is always full, not to rest, this sword of mine is always ready to fight.
My heart beats like it's about to burst
I'm trapped in a phobia for the future.
Even though I want to fight it
I'm still trapped.
I can't go there, where the soulless people are.
Fire can consume what it was born for, but not me. 

Image source: pexels Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art. With different editing tools.
